{
  "name": "RecentFile",
  "summary": "<p><strong>RecentFile</strong> 对象是 <strong>RecentFiles</strong> 集合的成员</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/RecentFiles/RecentFiles .htm#RecentFiles.RecentFiles\">RecentFiles</a></strong> (索引) （其中 <em>index</em> 是文件编号）返回 <strong>RecentFile</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例打开最近使用的文件列表中的第二个文件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Open</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果最近使用的文件列表中的第一个文件的名称为“example.xlsx”，则显示该文件的完整路径。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> recentFile = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (recentFile.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example.xlsx&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(recentFile.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Path</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表最近使用的文件列表中的某个文件。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表对象在其同类对象所组成的集合内的索引号。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近使用的文件列表中的第一个文件的索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近使用的文件列表中的最后一个文件的索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表对象的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近使用的文件列表中的第三个文件的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近使用的文件列表中的最后一个文件的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Path",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，该值代表此 <strong>RecentFile</strong> 对象表示的工作簿或文件的完整路径。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示最近使用的文件列表中的第一个文件的完整路径。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> recentFile = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(recentFile.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Path</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将最近使用的文件列表中的第三个文件的完整路径赋值到 A1 单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Path</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Delete",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除最近使用的文件列表中的第一个文件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果最近使用的文件的数量大于0，则删除最近使用过的第一个文件。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Open",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>打开一个最近使用的工作簿。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例打开最近使用的文件列表中的第二个工作簿。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Open</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果最近使用的文件列表中的第四个工作簿的名称为“example.xlsx”，则打开该工作簿。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> recentFile = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RecentFiles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (recentFile.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example.xlsx&quot;</span>) {\n        recentFile.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Open</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "<p>一个代表打开的工作簿的 Workbook 对象。</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}